    { "type": "text", "id": "key_h", "x": 20, "y": 1080, "width": 1920, "height": 28, "text": "Three things the bars are showing", "originalText": "Three things the bars are showing", "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#1e40af", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 290003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 290004, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },

    { "type": "text", "id": "key1_n", "x": 60, "y": 1130, "width": 30, "height": 28, "text": "①", "originalText": "①", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#b45309", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 291001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 291002, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },
    { "type": "text", "id": "key1_t", "x": 100, "y": 1130, "width": 580, "height": 100, "text": "Pending tail (gray cells)\nThe length of the gray prefix in each lane shows how long that req waited in pending_list. D's wait is the longest (6 iters) because the cap=2 forced it to queue behind the long-running B.", "originalText": "Pending tail (gray cells)\nThe length of the gray prefix in each lane shows how long that req waited in pending_list. D's wait is the longest (6 iters) because the cap=2 forced it to queue behind the long-running B.", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 291003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 291004, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.45 },

    { "type": "text", "id": "key2_n", "x": 720, "y": 1130, "width": 30, "height": 28, "text": "②", "originalText": "②", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#b45309", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 292001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 292002, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },
    { "type": "text", "id": "key2_t", "x": 760, "y": 1130, "width": 580, "height": 100, "text": "Yellow idle cells (prefill-first cost)\nWhen a prefill happens, all running reqs sit idle that iter (B in iter 1, 3, 6). This is the price of bsz=1 prefill — Lesson 8 (FlashAttention varlen) eliminates it by merging prefill into the decode batch.", "originalText": "Yellow idle cells (prefill-first cost)\nWhen a prefill happens, all running reqs sit idle that iter (B in iter 1, 3, 6). This is the price of bsz=1 prefill — Lesson 8 (FlashAttention varlen) eliminates it by merging prefill into the decode batch.", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 292003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 292004, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.45 },

    { "type": "text", "id": "key3_n", "x": 1380, "y": 1130, "width": 30, "height": 28, "text": "③", "originalText": "③", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#b45309", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 293001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 293002, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },
    { "type": "text", "id": "key3_t", "x": 1420, "y": 1130, "width": 510, "height": 100, "text": "Blue arrows = slot reuse\nThe instant A finishes at iter 2, _free_req_resources releases its slot+pages. Iter 3's prefill admits C into the SAME slot. Same trick C → D at iter 6.", "originalText": "Blue arrows = slot reuse\nThe instant A finishes at iter 2, _free_req_resources releases its slot+pages. Iter 3's prefill admits C into the SAME slot. Same trick C → D at iter 6.", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0, "seed": 293003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 293004, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.45 }
